msgid "kernel-of-the-week club"
msgstr "kernel-of-the-week club"

#: ../../K/kernel-of-the-week-club.rst:7
msgid ""
"The fictional society that :ref:`BSD` :ref:`bigot`\\s claim :ref:`Linux` "
"users belong to, alluding to the release-early-release-often style preferred"
" by the kernel maintainers. See :ref:`bazaar`\\. This was almost certainly "
"inspired by the earlier :ref:`bug-of-the-month-club`\\."
msgstr ""
":ref:`BSD`\\ の\\ :ref:`bigot`\\ たちが\\ :ref:`Linux`\\ "
"ユーザーを所属していると言い立てる架空の協会で、カーネル保守者が好むrelease-early-release-"
"often(早期に頻繁にリリースする)スタイルをほのめかしている。\\ :ref:`bazaar`\\ を参照。これはほぼ間違いなく、より古い\\ "
":ref:`bug-of-the-month-club`\\ に着想を得たものである。"
